{"tid":1303343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"市民投訴警察停車無熄匙，反被十幾個警察屈襲警 並反鎖拘捕 最後以公眾地方行為不檢罪名起訴................","createTime":"2019-07-10T09:39:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T14:35:36.000Z","uid":222970,"like":136,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"d2052a1feeb3cc80675c4f8ab941fbea670d388c","tid":1303343,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:39:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yIw_HGxBcdc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyIw_HGxBcdc&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC%2FsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=d3336eb5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yIw_HGxBcdc</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20141006/s00001/1412527960216/【短片】警駡酒店男-迫拍片者下跪拘捕\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20141006%2Fs00001%2F1412527960216%2F%E3%80%90%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87%E3%80%91%E8%AD%A6%E9%A7%A1%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E7%94%B7-%E8%BF%AB%E6%8B%8D%E7%89%87%E8%80%85%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%AA%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC%2FsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=d317957f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20141006%2Fs00001%2F1412527960216%2F%E3%80%90%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87%E3%80%91%E8%AD%A6%E9%A7%A1%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E7%94%B7-%E8%BF%AB%E6%8B%8D%E7%89%87%E8%80%85%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%AA%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95&h=6d314b38\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20141006/s00001/1412527960216/【短片】警駡酒店男-迫拍片者下跪拘捕</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其實當年依單野d黑警好撚癲<br />\n投訴冇熄匙有咩問題？<br />\n2:15果到黑警仲無啦啦推人仲禁止拍片<br />\n片都影埋 點解可以反屈轉頭？<br />\n<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n段中約10名警員包圍1名酒店職員，其中1名警員瘋狂辱駡酒店職員近2分鐘，更強迫在旁拍片男子跪下，再把他拘捕。警方發言人解釋，拍片男子涉多次叫囂及行為不檢，因此被捕。<br />\n<br />\n事發地點為新填地街逸豪酒店對出，周六晚上9時多，一名酒店男職員疑因不滿警方租用的旅遊巴停泊街上，沒有熄匙噴出廢氣，向司機投訴後，司機將旅遊巴駛離。<br />\n<br />\n片段中可見，一班警員圍着該名男職員，大叫「做完嘢涼吓冷氣都唔得？」警員又反問「警察出邊做完嘢，熱，係咪坐吓冷氣巴都詐形？」其中一名警員又稱自己工作壓力大，質疑該名男子針對警員，「想玩死差人？日日返12個鐘，瞓都無得瞓，仲要俾你玩？」<br />\n<br />\n一名男子在旁拍下整個過程，警員要求拍片者立即關機，並將他鎖上手銬，跪在地上接受調查，事後被捕帶返警署，不過整個過程被其他在場人士拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n警方發言人解釋，在新填地街拘捕24歲男子吳X豪，他是新填地街逸豪酒店職員，涉嫌多次叫囂，警員給予多次口頭警告後，以行為不檢罪名將其拘捕，已獲准保釋，10月下旬返署報到。"},{"pid":"62d7584a627d782fa8dafce9ac251071e726dcac","tid":1303343,"uid":25468,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:42:51.000Z","msg":"阿 sir 要嘆冷氣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ba96147c133b17b386b73f3fc5720949c807e9","tid":1303343,"uid":13867,"like":86,"dislike":1,"score":85,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:45:32.000Z","msg":"好撚on9<br />\n真係要死全家。<br />\n根本佢地除左制服真係一件垃圾，係人群中唔會敢認自己係咩職業<br />\n落單果時講自己做警_，一定比人圍罵"},{"pid":"9b1b55b5a80b8e07e3f98227399a8ed5b5084366","tid":1303343,"uid":31501,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:45:43.000Z","msg":"記得2014有好多警察自殺<br />\n唔知2019<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f4ad75a71a2456e34287dca6346d768f5ce09d1","tid":1303343,"uid":112748,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d2052a1feeb3cc80675c4f8ab941fbea670d388c","tid":1303343,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:39:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yIw_HGxBcdc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyIw_HGxBcdc&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC%2FsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=d3336eb5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yIw_HGxBcdc</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20141006/s00001/1412527960216/【短片】警駡酒店男-迫拍片者下跪拘捕\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20141006%2Fs00001%2F1412527960216%2F%E3%80%90%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87%E3%80%91%E8%AD%A6%E9%A7%A1%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E7%94%B7-%E8%BF%AB%E6%8B%8D%E7%89%87%E8%80%85%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%AA%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95&d